Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.91,0:23:02.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ever since then, I've been super-interested in the language of flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.30,0:23:06.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Talk to you later, Sonoko. Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.32,0:23:08.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.17,0:23:12.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here. I saw this at the flower shop, so I bought it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.79,0:23:15.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You bought that for me, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.96,0:23:17.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.24,0:23:21.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, what pretty peach blossoms!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.17,0:23:24.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm, this flower stands for...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.52,0:23:27.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"To be unrivaled in the world..."{this sounds awful. Catalan "invincible in fight". 天下無敵}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.05,0:23:33.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, what do you mean by this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.50,0:23:36.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.00,0:23:38.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just what do you mean,\N"to be unrivaled in the world"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.69,0:23:41.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.81,0:23:55.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.62,0:23:59.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's get outside before they get into the elevator!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.76,0:24:03.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No use running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.35,0:24:07.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What I want to say is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.25,0:24:09.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that you are an impostor!
